Chit-e5 hun-piat8 tek-khak tioh8 chiau3 Siong7-te3 e5 phiau-chun2. A-pek-lah8-han2 tioh8 li7-khui pun2-toe7, pun2-chok8, lau7-pe7 e5 ke, kap in oan5-choan5 hun-khui, kau3 i sou2 m7-bat e5 sou2-chai7 khi3. Mou5-se m7 seng5-jin7 choe3 Hoat-lo2 cha-bou2-kiaN2 e5 kiaN2; khah ai3 kap Siong7-te3 e5 peh-siN3 saN-kap siu7 khou2-lan7, m7 ai3 chiam7-si5 hiong2-siu7 choe7-ok e5 khoai3-lok8; liah8 choe3 u7 hun7 ti7 Ki-tok e5 leng5-jiok8, pi2 Ai-kip8 e5 chai5-po2 khah kui3-khi3. I2-sek-liat8 lang5 ia7-si7 an2-ni, Siong7-te3 keng2 in choe3 tai7-piau2 Siong7-te3 e5 bin5-chok8, sou2-i2 in tioh8 tui3 si3-piN e5 goa7-pang oan5-choan5 hun-piat8 chhut-lai5. I2-su-lah 9 chiuN, 10 chiuN kap Ni5-hi-bi2 13 chiuN u7 ka3-si7 lan2, siu7 keng2-soan2 e5 bin5-chok8, pho3-hoai7 hun-piat8 choe3 seng3 e5 kai3-han7, kap goa7-pang lang5 thong-hun, Siong7-te3 chiu7 bo5 lin5-bin2 khoan-iong5 in; in tioh8 li7-khui goa7-pang e5 lu2-chu2, koh chit8 pai2 giam5-keh che3-teng7 hun-piat8 e5 kai3-han7.
