“Lin2 chiah e5 im-hu7 ah, kiam2 m7 chai kap se3-kan choe3 peng5-iu2 si7 kap Siong7-te3 choe3 tui3-tek8 mah? Sou2-i2 kiN3-na7 ai3 choe3 se3-kan e5 peng5-iu2 e5, chiu7-si7 choe3 Siong7-te3 e5 tui3-tek8.” (Nga2-kok 4:4). Che si7 teh lun7 siok8-se3 e5 Ki-tok-tou5. ThiaN3 se3-kan e5 bo5 thiaN3 Siong7-te3 . ThiaN3 Siong7-te3 a2-si7 thiaN3 se3-kan, m7 si7 tui3 lan2 e5 heng5-ui5 lai5 phoaN3-toan3, si7 tui3 lan2 e5 sim-su i3-liam7; lan2 choe3 kah-i3 e5 si7 sim2-mih8, lai5 koat-teng7.
Chit e5 hun-piat8 choe3 seng3 si7 tui3 i2-ha7 3 tiam2 lai5 hun-piat8 e5:
1. Se3-kan E5 Ian3-lok8
“Tui3 sin3, Mou5-se i2-keng tiong2-seng5, m7 seng5-jin7 choe3 Hoat-lo2 cha-bou2-kiaN2 e5 kiaN2; khah ai3 kap Siong7-te3 e5 peh-siN3 saN-kap siu7 khou2-lan7, m7 ai3 chiam7-si5 hiong2-siu7 choe7-ok e5 khoai3-lok8; liah8-choe3 u7 hun7 Ki-tok e5 leng5-jiok8, pi2 Ai-kip8 e5 chai5-po2 khah kui3-khi3.” (Hi-pek-lai5 11:24~26). Che chiu7-si7 Mou5-se pang3-sak choe7-ok e5 khoai3-lok8 i2-au7 sou2 soan2-tek8 e5 lou7. Thiau3-bu2, khoaN3-hi3, poah8-kiau2, che long2 m7-si7 siok8 ti7 Siong7-te3 , si7 siok8 ti7 se3-kan. Siok8-leng5 e5 leng2-to7-chia2, seng3-tou5 choat8-tui3 boe7 kai3-siau7 chiah-e5; chi2-u7 hiah-e5 siok8-se3 e5 lang5 chiah ai3. Chit8 hong-bin7 ai3 beh hiong2-siu7 choe7-ok e5 khoai3-lok8, chit8 hong-bin7 siuN7 beh ki5-to2 choe3 kan-cheng3, che si7 put kho2-leng5 e5; ai3 ti7 choe7-ok tiong tui-kiu5 khoai3-lok8 e5 lang5 , i boe7 chham-ka ki5-to2-hoe7, koh-khah bo5-ai3 ti7 chu7-hoe7 chhut-siaN ki5-to2, tui3 kau3-hoe7 siok8-leng5 e5 kang-chok, chu7-jian5 ia7 long2 bo5 chhu3-bi7. Goa2 chhim-sin3 chin-chiaN3 e5 Ki-tok-tou5 it-teng7 goan7-i3 chun-than3 Siong7-te3 chiah-e5 hoan-hu3, chiu7-si7 “Boh8-tit kap m7 sin3 e5 lang5 choe3 phoaN7,” “Lin2 tioh8 tui3 in tiong-kan chhut-lai5, ka-ki7 hun-piat8.”
2. Kap Se3-kan Lian5-hap8
(1) Su7-giap8 siong7 e5 lian5-hap8: Ki-tok-tou5 na7 kap m7 sin3 e5 lang5 a2-si7 chia3 mia5 siok8-se3 e5 Ki-tok-tou5 tau5-chu eng5-giap8, si7 chin gui5-hiam2 e5 su7. I sui-jian5 u7 teh ki5-to2, chong2-si7, tui3 Siong7-te3 e5 Oe7 tit boe7 tioh8 se3-hok e5 eng3-un2, sou2-i2 chin-choe7 Ki-tok-tou5 e5 su7-giap8 boe7 hoat-tian2, koh sit-pai7. lang5 na7 bo5 thiaN-than3 Seng3-keng e5 ka3-si7, chai-e7 chiu7 tit8-tit8 lai5, Siong7-te3 thai2-tho2 oe7 su3-hok I sou2 hiam5 e5 lang5 ?
(2) Thong-hun: U7 chin-choe7 bo5 heng7-hok e5 hun-in, long2-si7 ui5-poe7 Siong7-te3 e5 Oe7 kap m7 sin3 e5 choe3 phoaN7 kau-poe5 e5 kiat-ko2. “Tok8-tok8 tioh8 ke3 siok8 Chu2 e5, chiah thang.” (I Ko-lim5-to 7:39). Che si7 Siong7-te3 e5 hoan-hu3. Na7 ke3 hou7 bo5 sin3 Chu2 e5 lang5 , kiat-ko2 it-teng7 sit-bang7; ui5-poe7 Siong7-te3 ka3-si7 e5 phoe3-hap8, Siong7-te3 thai2-tho2 oe7 su3-hok ti7 in e5 ka-teng5?
U7 chin-choe7 lu2-chu2, ui7-tioh8 beh kai2-koat chit e5 bun7-toe5, chiu7 kai2-tu5 hun-iok, chong2-si7 ia7 u7 chin-choe7 lu2-chu2 kou3-chip ka-ki7 e5 kian3-kai2, ui5-poe7 Siong7-te3 e5 ka3-si7, kiat-ko2 tu2-tioh8 choe7-choe7 kong2 boe7 chhut e5 thong3-khou2. Chit8 chiong2 lang5 beh the-si5 kong2, kap m7 sin3 e5 lang5 kiat-hun e5 bok8-tek, si7 beh in2-chhoa7 i lai5 sin3 Chu2; chi3-chio2 ti7 kiat-hun liau2-au7 ia7 oe7 pang-chan7 i, khou2-khng3 i sin3 Ia5-sou. Ki5-sit8 chit8 e5 lu2-chu2 na7 bo5 ti7 kiat-hun cheng5 in2-chhoa7 i e5 bi7-hun-hu lai5 sin3 Chu2, siuN7 beh ti7 kiat-hun liau2-au7 chiah in2-chhoa7 i, che seng5-kong e5 ki-hoe7 sit8-chai7 chin chio2.
Siong7-te3 e5 kang-lang5 ah! Toan3-toan3 m7-thang ui7-tioh8 ka-ki7 sou2 ai3 e5, lai5 ui5-poe7 Siong7-te3 e5 ka3-si7, tai7-seng kiam2-chhai2 oe7 kam2-kak chin khun3-lan5, chong2-si7, li2 tek-khak tioh8 chai-iaN2, Siong7-te3 ui7-tioh8 li2 e5 it-seng u7 koh-khah ho2 e5 an-pai5; thiaN-than3 I e5 ka3-si7 chiu7 an-choan5, hut-liok8 I e5 Oe7 chiu7 gui5-hiam2.
3. Se3-kan E5 Peng5-iu2
Siok8-se3 e5 peng5-iu2 tui3 Ki-tok-tou5 e5 ki5-to2 it-teng7 long2 bo5 chhu3-bi7; Siong7-te3 e5 kiaN2-ji5 ia7 m7 eng-kai tui-kiu5 siok8-se3 e5 gu5-lok8. Beh thit-tho5 he2 e5 lang5 kiam2 boe7 hou7 he2 sio tioh8 mah? Li2 kiam2-chhai2 beh kong2, Goa2 tioh8 pang3-sak in mah? Li2 m7-bian2 pang3-sak in, li2 na7 i7 siok8-leng5 e5 seng-oah8, in chiu7 chiam7-chiam7 kam2-kak tioh8 chhu3-bi7 bo5 saN-kang7, chu7-jian5 in chiu7 li7-khui li2. Tioh8 kap Siong7-te3 e5 kiaN2-ji5 choe3 peng5-iu2------bo5 lun7 cheng2-chok8, bo5 hun sek-ti7------long2 si7 ti7 Chu2 lai7-bin7 chiaN5-choe3 chit8-the2; kap in kau-poe5, it-teng7 pi2 kap bo5 sin3 e5 kut-jiok8 chi3-chhin koh-khah chhin-bit8. Ka-teng5 e5 lang5 kiam2-chhai2 boe7 liau2-kai2 li2; chong2-si7 ti7 Ki-tok thiaN3 e5 lai7-bin7, tak8-lang5 oe7 liau2-kai2 li2, oe7 tong5-cheng5 li2; chit-khoan2 e5 iu2-cheng5 eng2-oan2 boe7 toan7-choat8, chiu7-si7 kau3 si2 ia7 boe7 hou7 chit e5 iu2-cheng5 hun-khui. Sou2-i2 tioh8 kap hiah-e5 ti7 kim-se3, ia7 ti7 eng2-seng oe7 thang kap li2 saN-kap kau-poe5 e5 lang5 choe3 peng5-iu2.
Beh u7 hun-piat8 choe3 seng3 e5 seng-oah8 e5 pi3-koat, si7 chai7 ti7 siok8-leng5 pit8-sia5 kui-cheng3 e5 khui3-lat8. U7 chit8-e5 chhut-mia5 e5 lu2 koa-chhiu2, hoan2-hoe2 au7 bo5 ku2, u7 chit8-e5 chheng-lian5 lang5 phah tian7-oe7 beh iok i khi3 khoaN3-hi3, i long2 bo5 tiu5-tu5 chiu7 hoe5-tap kong2: Goa2 m7 khi3. In-ui7 ti7 chit8-bak8-nih ku2 e5 tiong-kan, “Ku7 e5 tai7-chi3 i2-keng ke3-khi3,” i long2 bo5 koh him-bou7 se3-kan e5 khoai3-lok8, “TaN long2 piN3-chiaN5 sin e5.” Ki-tok tiam3 ti7 i e5 sim, i chiu7 u7 sin e5 i3-ai3, i hoaN-hi2 chham-ka ki5-to2-hoe7, khia7 ti7 ke-lou7 chhiuN3-koa choe3 kan-cheng3, ai3 choe3 ko3-jin5 pou3-to7, ai3 chham-ka kau3-hoe7 tak8-hang7 chu7-hoe7. Ti7 i e5 sim-lai7 bo5 koh u7 kau-chian3, bo5 gi5-bun7, ia7 bo5 khun3-lan5. Ki-tok e5 hong-seng7 chhiong-moa2 i, se3-kan chiu7 the3-chhut.
Goa2 ti7 A-lah8-su-ka tui3 In3-te7-an lang5 thoan5-to7 e5 si5, goa2 chiah8 teng7 e5 piaN2 lai5 i5-chhi5 goa2 e5 seng-oah8. Bun5-beng5 lang5 kong2 hit e5 si7 kau2 teh chiah8 e5 piaN2. Goa2 tioh8 chiong i hang sio chiah oe7 thang chiah8, chong2-si7 hit si5-chun7 goa2 ia7 kam2-kak chin ho2-chiah8. Goa2 tng2-lai5 pun2-kok liau2-au7, u7 gu5-iu5 kap mi7-pau thang chiah8 kau3 chin pa2, goa2 chiu7 bo5 koh siuN7 beh chiah8 hiah-e5 teng7 e5 piaN2, in-ui7 goa2 i2-keng tit-tioh8 pi2 hiah-e5 koh-khah ho2 e5. Lan2 u7 tui3 Seng3 Sin5 teng5-thau5-siN e5 keng-giam7 koh tit-tioh8 Chu2 tiam3 ti7 sim-lai7, lan2 chiu7 oan5-choan5 boan2-chiok, boe7 koh him-bou7 se3-kan e5 mih8, an2-ni hun-piat8 choe3 seng3 chiu7 chin iong5-iN7 lah. Na7 u7 siok8-leng5 pit8-sia5 kui-cheng3 e5 khui3-lat8, beh ku7-choat8 ka-ki7 sou2 bo5 su-iau3 e5 tai7-chi3, chiu7 boe7 koh kam2-kak khun3-lan5 lah.
